{
  "stem": "3666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have a vision of having seen him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but we had heard that he is alive, and that's where he was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, we were separated by electric wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't touch the wire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were electrocuted right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't see him in the plane.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that point, we were separated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found out about him jumping off the train after the war when we met.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we stayed in the-- no, I don't think anybody worked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just an existence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beatings every day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you had to go to the toilet, they were standing there with the whips.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a door, let's say, the size of this room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And can you imagine, if you had to exit-- let's say in the morning, if you had to exit on the roll call, and people were trying-- they would-- they would stand.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The SS and kapos would stand with their whips.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whoever was inside got hit because this was their sport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Poles, Ukraines.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of Ukraines.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the worst, Lithuanians--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were hating the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were actually enjoying this whole scenario.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did it with--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, absolutely before, absolutely, I had heard later that these were criminals removed from the jail so they could take on this pleasant job.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that's-- they were-- the beatings were enormous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No reason.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at all, so it was there when they decided to transport us to another camp, and they separated again the children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew this was my final journey.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, yes, I was separated from my mother, and I knew that this is a death camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
